142
00:05:16.024 --> 00:05:17.692
Harder.
Yep.

143
00:05:17.775 --> 00:05:19.027
Harder.

144
00:05:19.110 --> 00:05:20.028
Oh.

145
00:05:20.111 --> 00:05:22.030
